			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BASIC CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move arrow -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Finalize selections / Launch the bubble -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X or Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Cancel selection -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square or Triangle Button</font>				  
                  <br>&nbsp; Finely tune aim to the left -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Finely tune aim to the right -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 Button</font>				  
                  <br>&nbsp; Toggles score display on/off -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L2 Button</font>	
                  <br>&nbsp; Displays L1/R1/L2 commands (when game is paused) -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R2 Button</font>					  
                  <br>&nbsp; Quit game (when game is paused) -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font>					  
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br><br>	
				  &nbsp;</td>
	 </tr>
	</table>
